WEBVTT

00:00:00.563 --> 00:00:03.081
So my name is Amy Webb,

00:00:03.105 --> 00:00:05.778
and a few years ago
I found myself at the end

00:00:05.802 --> 00:00:08.414
of yet another fantastic relationship

00:00:08.438 --> 00:00:11.526
that came burning down
in a spectacular fashion.

00:00:12.042 --> 00:00:14.778
And I thought, what's wrong with me?

00:00:14.802 --> 00:00:16.860
I don't understand
why this keeps happening.

00:00:16.884 --> 00:00:19.930
So I asked everybody in my life
what they thought.

00:00:20.383 --> 00:00:24.359
I turned to my grandmother,
who always had plenty of advice,

00:00:24.383 --> 00:00:27.351
and she said, "Stop being so picky.

00:00:27.375 --> 00:00:28.729
You've got to date around.

00:00:28.753 --> 00:00:30.107
And most importantly,